<p class="general_text">
    Paradroid is a self navigating, skydiving robot controlled by an onboard android handset. Simply choose your
    destination and throw it from a high place. Paradroid will skydive and navigate to your destination while sending
    online status reports. <br/>
    Paradroid has been tested and proven to work from heights of over 1000ft, dropped by a skydiver host.
</p>
