<p class="general_text">
    Paradroid started out as a project for Google Developer's day 2011 <em>"ADK challenge"</em>. The challenge called
    for developers to find creative ways to use Android's (then) new open accessory development api. This api allows for
    micro controllers to be connected to an android device and be used natively. <br/>
    Paradroid has received world wide attention and press coverage.
</p>

